ous . Every time I got in a Taxi, I stressed the one on Mankhool Street. Overall, I love my stay at this hotel. I love that I was minutes from two shopping by walking one was name AL Karama and the other one is at the front of the hotel. I'm sorry I forgot the name of it. You find plenty of fast food restaurants such as KFC,Burger King, and McDonalds. The only thing I was not able to get was a traditional Arabic meal and I love Arabic food.	
